snippet.textDisplay: Very interesting video Doc. Now I am wondering if giving Fluvoxamine with another med such as Molnupiravir would work even better at reducing symptoms of COVID-19? Anyway, thanks for keeping us up to date on treatments for COVID! Let's hope that they can get this under control sooner than later!
